evaluation.response:
I'm sorry to hear that, Frank. It sounds like you're feeling really overwhelmed by the small talk and the pressure to be social. Sometimes, it can feel like even the kindest gestures can be just too much. I care about you and I want to support you through this.&#x20;

You don't have to feel releasing to go through conversations that made you feel bad about yourself.



I'm here to listen if you want to chat further about your feelings.
